Description: Poor Naruto: he must cope with a ninja summit and a target on the back of his good friend, Sasuke.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 49
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy. How will she survive the pursuit of demons who want the power in her blood?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 6
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: From the publisher: "Get ready to brush up on world history with these handsome and hysterical personifications of the Axis Powers as they meet, become friends and form one of the most powerful alliances the world has ever seen."
Title: HETALIA AXIS POWERS, VOL. 1
Author: Hidekaz Himaruya

Description: The next generation of Yu-Gi-Oh battle it out at the Duel Academy. In this volume, the two best students, Jaden and Chazz, compete.
Title: YU-GI-OH! GX, VOL. 5
Author: Kazuki Takahashi and Naoyuki Kageyama
Contributor: by Kazuki Takahashi and Naoyuki Kageyama

Description: Isn’t being a kid hard enough? For this group, who are also part bird, nothing comes easy. An F.B.I. agent steps in to help, but the evil "erasers" lurk around the corner.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE, VOL. 3
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee

Description: Kagome, a modern-day high school girl, is pulled into Japan’s ancient past, where she is linked to a dog-eared half demon named Inuyasha. In this volume: evil lurks in the form of Magatsuhi.
Title: INUYASHA, VOL. 53
Author: Rumiko Takahashi

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called "One Piece." In this volume, Luffy gets help from some former foes in an attempt to rescue his brother.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 55
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH,  VOL. 32
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Is there a love triangle in bloom? Thanks to a burglary, Teru is staying at Kurosaki’s apartment. Then a woman from his past, Riko, shows up. Uh oh.
Title: DENGEKI DAISY, VOL. 2
Author: Kyousuke Motomi

Description: Alice wanders into a very different part of Wonderland in this interpretation of the classic tale. In this new area of the fantasy land, every man is in love with Alice... and firearms.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS, VOL. 4
Author: Quinrose and Hoshino Soumei
